      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ、これが私達の空気だよ、こころちゃん\nあ、そうだ、そろそろあのことを……",
      "startTime": 181.7333420155,
